{"tid":1609460,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果你當年偷人mp3 依家做緊犬 突然比對家黑衫屌 有乜感想","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:48:23.000Z","uid":242537,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b149c0050a65307a673202533923de8e84f9385b","tid":1609460,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防暴警被中學同學認出: 偷我MP3，宜家做警察!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9.29全球 #反極權 大遊行開始前，大批防暴警察駐守銅鑼灣多個地帶。期間竟然發生一場中學同學的相遇⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n一名防暴警察被另一名黑衫男子認出為自己的中學同學，更指該名防暴警察曾經在中學偷取自的MP3播放器。雖然該防暴警察稱「唔好亂講嘢」，但黑衫男子叫喊「返中學囉」。最後該防暴由上級調離現場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71021587_924188057980247_4179525382606684160_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmTs7e0FQdL_GCI0vaDyPv_Un_NPil6h7qq0F1p-NAS9E-FCGkM4lSof0grly6BSrU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=c7471e7cbc088ded0280d27e4737c0e5&amp;oe=5E2E8BDE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71021587_924188057980247_4179525382606684160_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmTs7e0FQdL_GCI0vaDyPv_Un_NPil6h7qq0F1p-NAS9E-FCGkM4lSof0grly6BSrU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dc7471e7cbc088ded0280d27e4737c0e5%26oe%3D5E2E8BDE&h=cec41bd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"174fd0824af04f7ed1cb127f07acd2d3d3b009a1","tid":1609460,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e84a8bb40da